    <item>
      <title>eZ Extension Builder 0.2 (pake-based) released</title>
      <link>http://projects.ez.no/ezextensionbuilder/news/ez_extension_builder_0_2_pake_based_released</link>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;
*General:&lt;br /&gt;
. changed task execution order: now all 'check' tasks are run before any 'file changing' tasks&lt;br /&gt;
. allow more flexibility in naming the .sql files&lt;br /&gt;
. check for minimum pake version when not using bundled version&lt;br /&gt;
. when upgrading, upgrade also the bundled pake version&lt;br /&gt;
. find extension name, if not specified on cli, even when pake/options-ezextensionbuilder.yaml is present besides options-extension.yaml&lt;br /&gt;
*Bugfixes:&lt;br /&gt;
. on windows allow to find doxygen if not specified as cli option&lt;br /&gt;
. the .tar.gz files built on windows would not open fine on mac/unix (cuz' of backslash in pathnames)&lt;br /&gt;. fix a fatal error in tool-upgrade-check task&lt;/p&gt;</description>
      <author>community@ez.no (Gaetano Giunta)</author>
      <guid>http://projects.ez.no/ezextensionbuilder/news/ez_extension_builder_0_2_pake_based_released</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 28 Apr 2011 13:31:05 +0000</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>eZ Extension Builder 0.1 (pake-based) released</title>
      <link>http://projects.ez.no/ezextensionbuilder/news/ez_extension_builder_0_1_pake_based_released</link>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;The tool has been rewritten from scratch, and it is both more flexible and more powerful than the original version.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;It is now based on Pake (a "make" lookalike written in php), and has no more need for ANT or Java.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;It can boostrap quite easily, just:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ol&gt;

&lt;li&gt;download the script: wget http://svn.projects.ez.no/ezextensionbuilder/stable/pake/pakefile.php&lt;/li&gt;

&lt;li&gt;run it: php pakefile.php&lt;/li&gt;

&lt;/ol&gt;
&lt;p&gt;It is quite well documented, and should not be too hard to use.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
      <author>community@ez.no (Gaetano Giunta)</author>
      <guid>http://projects.ez.no/ezextensionbuilder/news/ez_extension_builder_0_1_pake_based_released</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 13 Apr 2011 16:26:53 +0000</pubDate>
    </item>
